login_email_auction_to_friend_title~==~Mail Auction to A Friend Login
login_email_auction_to_friend_help~==~Login to email this auction item to your friend. You must be a registered user before you can use this service. If you are not registered please go to new user <!--CLASS::Registration-->.
login_email_auction_to_friend_user_id_label~==~Your User ID:
login_email_auction_to_friend_password_label~==~Your Password:
login_email_auction_to_friend_remember_login_label~==~Remember username and password for future logins?
login_email_auction_to_friend_submit_button~==~Login
mail_auction_title~==~E-mail Auction Item to A Friend
mail_auction_help~==~Please send these e-mails only to people you know who would be interested in the item. If someone asks you not to send these e-mails to them, please comply.<br><br><b>Sellers:</b><br> If you use this service to advertise an item that you are selling, and a recipient complains to <!--CLASS::Site_Name-->, your registration may be suspended.
friend_email_label~==~<b>Your friend's e-mail address </b><br>(will not be used for promotional purposes nor disclosed to a third party):
optional_message_label~==~Personal message to your friend <font color = red>(optional)</font>
optional_message~==~I saw this item for sale at <!--CLASS::Site_Name-->, the world's largest personal trading community, and thought that you might be interested.
email_auction_to_friend_subject~==~Auction Item Will Interest You
friend_email_body~==~Here is the item details: Item #:<!--Item_ID-->, <BR>Title: <!--Title-->, <BR>Quantity: <!--Quantity-->, <BR>Start Time: <!--Start_Time-->, <BR>End Time: <!--End_Time-->, <BR>Start Bid: <!--Start Bid-->, <BR>Bid Increment: <!--Bid_Increment-->, Location: <!--Location-->, Country: <!--Country-->, Language: <!--Language-->, Home Page: <!--Home Page-->, Description: <!--Description-->. CLick on this link to go to this site now: <!--Link--> . Thank you. The Auction Team
email_sent~==~Auction Emailed
email_sent_help~==~The Auction item information sent to your friend as you requested.
invalid_email~==~Invalid Email Address
invalid_email_help~==~ The firend email address you entered is not valid address, Please make sure to use a correct email address if you want really to send this Auction information.
submit_email_auction_button~==~<A HREF="#" onclick="document.Email_Friend.submit(); return false;"><B>Send it</B></A>
reset_email_auction_button~==~<A HREF="#" onclick="document.Email_Friend.reset(); return false;"><B>Reset</B></A>
cancel_email_auction_button~==~<A HREF="javascript:history.go(-1)"><b>Cancel</b></A>
item_id_label~==~Item # 